{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":42,"text":"I was one of the only kids in college who had a reason"},{"time":2791,"text":"to go to the P.O. box at the end of the day,"},{"time":5356,"text":"and that was mainly because my mother has never believed"},{"time":7708,"text":"in email, in Facebook, in texting or cell phones in general."},{"time":11385,"text":"And so while other kids were BBM-ing their parents,"},{"time":13940,"text":"I was literally waiting by the mailbox"},{"time":17081,"text":"to get a letter from home to see how the weekend had gone,"},{"time":19769,"text":"which was a little frustrating when Grandma was in the hospital,"},{"time":22157,"text":"but I was just looking for some sort of scribble,"},{"time":26502,"text":"some unkempt cursive from my mother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29133,"text":"And so when I moved to New York City after college"},{"time":31538,"text":"and got completely sucker-punched in the face by depression,"},{"time":34498,"text":"I did the only thing I could think of at the time."},{"time":37250,"text":"I wrote those same kinds of letters that my mother had written me"},{"time":40262,"text":"for strangers, and tucked them all throughout the city,"},{"time":43675,"text":"dozens and dozens of them. I left them everywhere,"},{"time":46518,"text":"in cafes and in libraries, at the U.N., everywhere."},{"time":50720,"text":"I blogged about those letters and the days"},{"time":52775,"text":"when they were necessary, and I posed"},{"time":54749,"text":"a kind of crazy promise to the Internet:"},{"time":57412,"text":"that if you asked me for a hand-written letter,"},{"time":59798,"text":"I would write you one, no questions asked."},{"time":63119,"text":"Overnight, my inbox morphed into this harbor of heartbreak --"},{"time":67195,"text":"a single mother in Sacramento, a girl being bullied"},{"time":69886,"text":"in rural Kansas, all asking me, a 22-year-old girl"},{"time":73806,"text":"who barely even knew her own coffee order,"},{"time":76452,"text":"to write them a love letter and give them a reason"},{"time":78998,"text":"to wait by the mailbox."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81327,"text":"Well, today I fuel a global organization"},{"time":84151,"text":"that is fueled by those trips to the mailbox,"},{"time":86827,"text":"fueled by the ways in which we can harness social media"},{"time":89457,"text":"like never before to write and mail strangers letters"},{"time":92947,"text":"when they need them most, but most of all,"},{"time":95804,"text":"fueled by crates of mail like this one, my trusty mail crate,"},{"time":99100,"text":"filled with the scriptings of ordinary people,"},{"time":103340,"text":"strangers writing letters to other strangers not because"},{"time":106041,"text":"they're ever going to meet and laugh over a cup of coffee,"},{"time":108832,"text":"but because they have found one another by way of letter-writing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112444,"text":"But, you know, the thing that always gets me"},{"time":113958,"text":"about these letters is that most of them have been written"},{"time":117494,"text":"by people that have never known themselves loved on a piece of paper."},{"time":122198,"text":"They could not tell you about the ink of their own love letters."},{"time":125903,"text":"They're the ones from my generation,"},{"time":127772,"text":"the ones of us that have grown up into a world"},{"time":130638,"text":"where everything is paperless, and where some"},{"time":133721,"text":"of our best conversations have happened upon a screen."},{"time":136783,"text":"We have learned to diary our pain onto Facebook,"},{"time":139141,"text":"and we speak swiftly in 140 characters or less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143431,"text":"But what if it's not about efficiency this time?"},{"time":146103,"text":"I was on the subway yesterday with this mail crate,"},{"time":148932,"text":"which is a conversation starter, let me tell you."},{"time":151338,"text":"If you ever need one, just carry one of these. (Laughter)"},{"time":153647,"text":"And a man just stared at me, and he was like,"},{"time":156480,"text":"\"Well, why don't you use the Internet?\""},{"time":158969,"text":"And I thought, \"Well, sir, I am not a strategist,"},{"time":162442,"text":"nor am I specialist. I am merely a storyteller.\""},{"time":166208,"text":"And so I could tell you about a woman"},{"time":168889,"text":"whose husband has just come home from Afghanistan,"},{"time":171799,"text":"and she is having a hard time unearthing this thing called conversation,"},{"time":175345,"text":"and so she tucks love letters throughout the house"},{"time":177805,"text":"as a way to say, \"Come back to me."},{"time":179933,"text":"Find me when you can.\""},{"time":181491,"text":"Or a girl who decides that she is going to leave love letters"},{"time":184413,"text":"around her campus in Dubuque, Iowa, only to find"},{"time":187672,"text":"her efforts ripple-effected the next day when she walks out"},{"time":190725,"text":"onto the quad and finds love letters hanging"},{"time":192860,"text":"from the trees, tucked in the bushes and the benches."},{"time":196973,"text":"Or the man who decides that he is going to take his life,"},{"time":200006,"text":"uses Facebook as a way to say goodbye"},{"time":203145,"text":"to friends and family."},{"time":204498,"text":"Well, tonight he sleeps safely with a stack of letters"},{"time":207068,"text":"just like this one tucked beneath his pillow,"},{"time":210285,"text":"scripted by strangers who were there for him when."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213604,"text":"These are the kinds of stories that convinced me"},{"time":215969,"text":"that letter-writing will never again need to flip back her hair"},{"time":218815,"text":"and talk about efficiency, because she is an art form now,"},{"time":222420,"text":"all the parts of her, the signing, the scripting, the mailing,"},{"time":225813,"text":"the doodles in the margins."},{"time":228351,"text":"The mere fact that somebody would even just sit down,"},{"time":231485,"text":"pull out a piece of paper and think about someone"},{"time":233152,"text":"the whole way through, with an intention that is so much"},{"time":235798,"text":"harder to unearth when the browser is up and the iPhone"},{"time":239028,"text":"is pinging and we've got six conversations rolling in at once,"},{"time":242555,"text":"that is an art form"},{"time":243990,"text":"that does not fall down to the Goliath of \"get faster,\""},{"time":247165,"text":"no matter how many social networks we might join."},{"time":250037,"text":"We still clutch close these letters to our chest,"},{"time":252882,"text":"to the words that speak louder than loud,"},{"time":255516,"text":"when we turn pages into palettes to say the things"},{"time":257873,"text":"that we have needed to say,"},{"time":259439,"text":"the words that we have needed to write, to sisters"},{"time":262127,"text":"and brothers and even to strangers, for far too long."},{"time":265649,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":269215,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}